# REAL-TIME DATA & FINANCIAL CLARITY

This update focuses on making the dashboard more "alive" with live market data and shifting from percentage-based metrics to actual dollar profits for better financial tracking.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Profit Display:** All P/L displays (Dashboard and Journal) will now show the absolute dollar amount (e.g., **+$100.50**) instead of **+3.5%**. This provides a more immediate sense of your actual gains and losses.

> [!TIP]
> **Live Market Data:** I will integrate a **TradingView Ticker Widget** to show real-time prices for **BTC/USDT**, **ETH/USDT**, and **SOL/USDT** directly in your dashboard. This saves you from switching tabs constantly.

